# CFC Bakery — Backtest & Business Sim (Phase 6)

Rolling-origin, 3 expanding folds: 2026-04, 2026-05, 2026-06. Retrained per fold.
Test rows pooled: 608,261.

## Accuracy — point forecast (pooled, volume-weighted WMAPE)

| Model | WMAPE | MAE | Bias |
|---|---|---|---|
| LGBM P50 | 0.341 | 2.29 | -0.41 |
| moving_avg_7 | 0.405 | 2.72 | +0.15 |
| naive_lag1 | 0.453 | 3.04 | +0.16 |
| seasonal_naive_7 | 0.537 | 3.60 | +0.26 |
| dow_mean_28 | 0.468 | 3.14 | +0.25 |

**LGBM P50 vs floor: 0.341 vs 0.405 (+16%).** Stretch target ≤0.321.

